title: Estonia Unemployed Persons
description: The number of unemployed persons in Estonia increased to 48.42 Thousand in October of 2022 from 47.40 Thousand in September of 2022. Unemployed Persons in Estonia averaged 37.97 Thousand from 1993 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 95 Thousand in March of 2010 and a record low of 12 Thousand in October of 2006. In Estonia, unemployed persons are individuals who are without a job and actively seeking to work. This page provides - Estonia Unemployed Persons - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Estonia
